column2: Illini Media never shares personally identifiable information provided to us online in ways unrelated to the ones described above without also providing you an opportunity to opt-out or otherwise prohibit such unrelated uses. Google or any ad server may use information (not including your name, address, email address or telephone number) about your visits to this and other websites in order to provide advertisements about goods and services of interest to you.
To opt-out    You may use Google Analytics' currently available opt-outs at any time.
